column3: For a limited time, you can relive this event via the Seasonal Event Replay feature.
Do you wish to replay the event?

If you proceed, the following quest(s) will be rendered incomplete:

</If><If(Equal(IntegerParameter(4),0))><Else/>The following NPC(s) will become unavailable for trade until you have completed the requisite quest again:
